{"tid":647650,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"點解最近多左咁多大快活打手","createTime":"2018-04-30T04:31:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T04:03:11.000Z","uid":10325,"like":12,"dislike":106,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"97fb657a227ab966b158186a9dfc575b4c84ee34","tid":647650,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T04:31:27.000Z","msg":"用33$學生餐雞脾飯做例子<br />\n以下全部用成本價計<br />\n<br />\n1. 雞脾當當佢成本 $20一件 <br />\n<br />\n2. 紅豆冰出面賣都要 $15 杯<br />\n我當佢入貨價 $14 好未 ???（未計冰）<br />\n<br />\n3. 雜菜 呢個比較難預 因為佢一大箱咁入貨<br />\n我當佢成本 $5 份 <br />\n<br />\n4. 仲有呀 豆 紅蘿蔔<br />\n呢到無5$走唔甩啦<br />\n<br />\n5. 飯 當佢5$<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTotal Cost = $20+$14+$5+$5+$5 =49 &gt; $33<br />\n<br />\n仲未計埋 d 燈油火蠟 人工 清潔水費咁賣法 大快活咪蝕住黎做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以咁多打手都唔係冇道理喎 <br />\n<br />\n利伸：非打手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/123026_8a57f1ded6c02f41a5b372652b9c3077.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F123026_8a57f1ded6c02f41a5b372652b9c3077.png&h=6811c8f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f91b4cade26eadedd47d41cfdb0f7e3b59fbd121","tid":647650,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T04:33:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116eda3ed702acac3cf1a7e6d3ef69aa21258bff","tid":647650,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T04:38:27.000Z","msg":"邊個負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fe5e4bfc3ba4d3cc290d20d6f9135bee8726731","tid":647650,"uid":65408,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T04:45:49.000Z","msg":"你所指嘅「成本」係包d乜？"},{"pid":"9988b5d3e69fe4c50547e7793e1eeb4af0f0f839","tid":647650,"uid":6677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T04:47:25.000Z","msg":"0分重作"},{"pid":"c0d5eb83c56037e194d5261bbc